<hw>D.O.T.</hw></mhw>
<pr>(d⟦emac⟧"⟦omac⟧*t⟦emac⟧`)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The United
States Department of Transportation.</def> <mark>[acronym]</mark>
<note>The Department of Transportation promulgates standards for the
strength of shipping containers, and this abgreviation is often seen on
cardboard boxes.</note>⟦br⟧
